  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Operations Executive",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Operations Executive</strong></u><br />The Operations Executive will support the Sales & Marketing Manager in managing day-to-day operations and creative support. The ideal candidate is organized, proactive, and comfortable working across operations, coordination, and creative tasks.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p><u>Operations & Project Support</u></p><ul><li>Support the Sales & Marketing Manager in executing operational plans </li><li>Coordinate with internal teams, vendors, and partners to ensure smooth project implementation</li><li>Track operational timelines, deliverables, and follow-ups</li></ul><p><u>Menu Management & Coordination</u></p><ul><li>Assist with menu uploads to internal systems/platforms</li><li>Coordinate with relevant stakeholders (kitchen, vendors, schools) to ensure menu accuracy and updates</li><li>Ensure timely updates and resolve basic operational issues related to menus</li></ul><p><u>Sales & Marketing Support</u></p><ul><li>Provide administrative and operational support to sales and marketing initiatives</li><li>Assist in preparing basic reports, presentations, and coordination for campaigns</li></ul><p><u>A&P / Creative Suppor</u>t</p><ul><li>Assist the A&P (Advertising & Promotion) team with creative tasks, including:</li></ul><ol><li>Basic video recording and photography</li><li>Supporting content creation for marketing materials</li><li>Coordinating simple design needs with internal or external designers</li></ol><ul><li>Help organize and manage creative assets (photos, videos, files)</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Requirements & Qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or bachelor’s degree in business, Marketing, Operations, or a related field</li><li>1 year of experience in operations, marketing support, or coordination roles (<em>fresh graduates may be considered)</em></li><li>Familiarity with basic design or content tools is a plus</li></ul><p><strong>Skills & Attributes</strong></p><ul><li>Good communication and teamwork abilities</li><li>Detail-oriented and able to manage multiple tasks</li><li>Proactive, hands-on, and willing to learn</li><li>Able to work in a fast-paced, project-based environment</li></ul>",
